{"type":null,"faqId":46040,"title":"无法使用离线导航，怎么解决？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、检查GPS开关是否打开，定位模式选择：准确度高，使用GPS、WLAN和移动网络定位（手机的“设置--位置服务”的勾选项全部勾选打开）；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、请在华为应用市场，下载最新的第三方导航软件，建议使用高德地图或者百度地图；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、检查所在城市离线地图是否下载完整，建议先打开数据连接搜索到目的地之后，规划好路线，再断开网络，上路进行离线导航；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4、无SIM卡WLAN网络连接状态下，请检查数据业务是否可用；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5、隧道中发现导航图标停止了，是因为隧道中无法搜索到卫星，请耐心等到出隧道之后，开车到空旷路面重新导航；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>6、请保证设备在电量充足、温度较低情况下工作。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1820","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444375610000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":22,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"离线,地图,导航","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}